<h3>Tutorial 10. Preparing the Fabric Cup Cover.</h3>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Below are our prepared cup pieces.</strong> I have decided to duplicate them with very thin iron-on fabric. </p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/wedding%20dresses/wedding%203/transcript/Tutorial%2010_files/image002.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
