<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/wedding%20dresses/wedding%203/transcript/Tutorial%2010_files/image004.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/wedding%20dresses/wedding%203/transcript/Tutorial%2010_files/image006.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Now we can safely join the pieces.</strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
<img src="https://corsetacademy.s3.amazonaws.com/wedding%20dresses/wedding%203/transcript/Tutorial%2010_files/image008.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block"></strong></p>

